== 慈善活動 ==


舒馬克是[[聯合國教科文組織|聯合國教科文組織]]的特別大使，捐出了150萬[[歐元|歐元]]<ref name="unesco-champion for sport">{{cite web| url = http://portal.unesco.org/en/ev.php-URL_ID=6691&URL_DO=DO_TOPIC&URL_SECTION=201.html| title = Michael Schumacher, a UNESCO champion| accessdate = 2006-10-25| date = 2002| work = | publisher = UNESCO| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070221113842/http://portal.unesco.org/en/ev.php-URL_ID%3D6691%26URL_DO%3DDO_TOPIC%26URL_SECTION%3D201.html| archivedate = 2007-02-21}}</ref>。此外亦喜歡踢[[足球|足球]]，效力當地球隊FC Echichens<ref>{{cite news | title = Schumi urged to lace up his boots | publisher = Wheels24 | date = 2006-10-25 | url = http://www.wheels24.co.za/Wheels24/NewsPics/0,,1369-1375_2020222,00.html | accessdate = 2006-11-01 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070612192337/http://www.wheels24.co.za/Wheels24/NewsPics/0,,1369-1375_2020222,00.html | archivedate = 2007-06-12 }}</ref>，他亦參與多項慈善足球活動<ref name="fifa-charity football">{{cite news |title=FIFA Fair Play: Playing for a better world |url=http://www.fifa.com/en/fairplay/index/0,1255,104749,00.html?articleid=104749 |publisher=FIFA.com |date=2004-12-16 |accessdate=2006-10-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060918063721/http://www.fifa.com/en/fairplay/index/0%2C1255%2C104749%2C00.html?articleid=104749 |archivedate=2006-09-18 }}</ref>以及一級方程式車手之間足球比賽交流<ref name="schumacher retirement response thoughts">{{cite news |title = Thoughts on Schumacher |url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/motorsport/formula_one/5330382.stm |work =  |publisher = BBC Sport |date = 2006-09-10 |accessdate = 2006-10-25 |archive-date = 2007-05-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070507134642/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/motorsport/formula_one/5330382.stm |dead-url = no }}</ref>，更經常有進球。

2004年印度洋大地震（一般簡稱[[印度洋海嘯|印度洋海嘯]]或南亞海嘯），舒馬赫捐出了1000萬美元，成為全世界以個人名義捐款者裡，金額最高的一位。<ref name="Schumacher makes tsunami charity pledge">{{cite web| url = http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2005/1/2519.html| title = Schumacher makes tsunami charity pledge| accessdate = 2005-01-05| date = 2005| work = | publisher = The Official Formula 1 Website| archive-date = 2014-08-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140805233023/http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2005/1/2519.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 軼事 ==
2007年12月，舒马赫搭乘計程车時为了赶飞机，在計程车司机允許下，由舒马赫自己親自駕駛計程车，将自己和家人按时送到机场。據計程車司機複述，當時舒马赫展示神乎其技的駕駛技術，衝過一些一般人認為不可能的地方，使得計程車司機也為之驚訝，計程車司機展示舒马赫為他所簽的名，也說舒马赫為人豪爽，給了他不錯的小費，但他拒絕向傳媒透露舒马赫當時駕駛的車速。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://auto.163.com/07/1213/14/3VJNTEJ4000827U2.html |title=车王舒马赫为赶飞机客串速度最快"的哥"(图) |publisher=网易新闻  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071216025611/http://auto.163.com/07/1213/14/3VJNTEJ4000827U2.html |archivedate=2007-12-16 }}</ref>

